         <titleStmt>
            <title>Maṣḥafa bǝrhān ‘Book of Light’, Tǝmhǝrta hāymānot ‘Teaching of the Faith’
               Hāymānotu la-Yāʿqob ʾƎlbarādi ‘The Faith of Jacob Baradeus’, Maṣḥafa baqʷǝʿet
               ʾǝm-dǝrsāna bahlu la-qǝddus ʾabbā Wagris ‘Book of Sufficiency from the Treatise of
               Sayings of Saint ʾAbba Evagrius’,  Mǝʿdan baʾǝnta sammǝntu ḫǝllināt za-ʾabba Wagris
               ‘Treatise on the Eight Thoughts (of Evilness) by ʾAbba Evagrius’, Excerpt from the
               Collectio Monastica, Miscellaneous prayers and hymns</title>
